{
  "_comment": [
    "Custom Links — appended to / merged into the built-in Links menu.",
    "",
    "This file is managed via Admin > UI tab > Custom Menu Links,",
    "or you can edit it directly and restart the server.",
    "",
    "HOW MERGING WORKS",
    "─────────────────",
    "Each entry in 'groups' is matched against the built-in groups in",
    "frontend-pages.json by the 'group' name (case-sensitive).",
    "",
    "  • If the name MATCHES a built-in group, your files/subgroups are",
    "    injected INTO that group — they appear alongside the built-in links.",
    "",
    "  • If the name does NOT match any built-in group, a brand-new group",
    "    is appended AFTER all built-in groups in the menu.",
    "",
    "SUPPORTED FIELDS",
    "────────────────",
    "Group level:",
    "  group      (required) — display name; must match a built-in group name",
    "                          to inject into it, or be unique to create a new group.",
    "  depends_on (optional) — hide this group if the named feature is disabled.",
    "                          Known keys: cw_skimmer, noise_floor, digital_decodes,",
    "                                      rotator, ant_switch.",
    "                          Only meaningful on NEW groups (built-in group",
    "                          visibility is controlled by the built-in config).",
    "  files      (optional) — array of direct links shown in this group.",
    "  subgroups  (optional) — array of named sub-menus, each with their own files.",
    "",
    "File / link level:",
    "  path        (required) — relative path (e.g. 'mypage.html') or full URL",
    "                           (https://...). Relative paths are served from the",
    "                           UberSDR web root.",
    "  name        (required) — label shown in the menu.",
    "  description (optional) — tooltip text shown on hover.",
    "  depends_on  (optional) — hide this link if the named feature is disabled.",
    "",
    "Subgroup level:",
    "  name  (required) — display name. If it matches an existing built-in subgroup",
    "                     name, files are injected into that subgroup.",
    "  files (optional) — array of link entries (same fields as above).",
    "",
    "EXAMPLES (add to the groups array below to activate):",
    "",
    "  Inject a link into an existing built-in group:",
    "  { \"group\": \"Propagation Conditions\", \"files\": [",
    "      { \"path\": \"https://prop.example.com/\", \"name\": \"My Propagation Tool\",",
    "        \"description\": \"Custom propagation analysis tool.\" }",
    "  ]}",
    "",
    "  Create a brand-new group:",
    "  { \"group\": \"My Station\", \"files\": [",
    "      { \"path\": \"https://www.qrz.com/db/M0XYZ\", \"name\": \"QRZ Page\" },",
    "      { \"path\": \"https://hamlog.example.com/\", \"name\": \"Log Book\" }",
    "  ]}",
    "",
    "  New group with a depends_on (only shown when CW Skimmer is enabled):",
    "  { \"group\": \"Local Resources\", \"depends_on\": \"cw_skimmer\", \"files\": [",
    "      { \"path\": \"https://cluster.example.com/\", \"name\": \"Local DX Cluster\" }",
    "  ]}",
    "",
    "  Inject a new subgroup into an existing built-in group:",
    "  { \"group\": \"Clients\", \"subgroups\": [",
    "      { \"name\": \"My Tools\", \"files\": [",
    "          { \"path\": \"https://mytool.example.com/\", \"name\": \"My Custom Tool\" }",
    "      ]}",
    "  ]}",
    "",
    "The '_comment' key is ignored by the server."
  ],
  "groups": []
}
